# Line-ending policy for the Elite:Dangerous Black Book.
#
# Store ALL text files as LF in the repository and check them out as LF on disk.
# This repo is authored from WSL/Linux and deployed to GitHub Pages, so LF is the
# canonical form everywhere. Git normalizes on commit, so a CRLF working copy no
# longer produces spurious whole-file diffs.
#
# Re-normalize after editing this file with:  git add --renormalize .

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize or diff as text.
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.webp  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.xlsx  binary
*.pdf   binary
